00:00:08.000 --> 00:00:10.000
En ze waren ontzettend leuk.

00:00:10.000 --> 00:00:12.000
Ray was degene in de familie die de ampersands droeg.

00:00:12.000 --> 00:00:15.000
(Gelach)

